### Paid REST smoke
# Run from PowerShell instead of pasting X-PAYMENT manually:
# npm run test:paid

### MCP - initialize (free)
POST http://localhost:3000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": { "name": "test-client", "version": "1.0.0" }
  }
}

### MCP - unpaid preflight_assess Sepolia transfer (expected 402)
POST http://localhost:3000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 5,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "preflight_assess",
    "arguments": {
      "from": "0x1ad4C9d7CEa32B44cd54260A52C57B6Ce4e0D6eB",
      "to": "0x8E159C52Dc2823cB6728E26898A2bABC286BBAc7",
      "data": "0x",
      "value": "1000000000000000",
      "chainId": 11155111
    }
  }
}
